[{"Name":"Rudi Ts.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUBhzdHxVXNESBshrB5X001eC3wpDujz21I0UG6JQZLMIY7AyeO6g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've been coming to this hipster spot regularly with the guys for quite some time now, and it never disappoints. Even though we may raise the average age a bit, the atmosphere is always lively, with a fun Ashdodi crowd adding to the vibe. The music is excellent, perfectly complementing the great food and drinks they offer. The service is always on pointâ€”friendly and attentive. On top of that, the prices are affordable, making it a fantastic spot to unwind. Highly recommended!

Tip: If itâ€™s your first time here, start with the Chiburekiâ€”it's a nostalgic dish from when the place was a small joint selling just that. What I usually go for (and it never disappoints) is the nuggets made in beer, fries with cheddar cheese, and the haloumi salad, which is quite big. We always pair it with a Franziskaner beer on tap.

We usually come on Thursdays around 21:30 when there are still plenty of tables available, but the place fills up fast as the night goes on. It's a good idea to either call ahead and reserve a table or arrive a bit earlier to secure a spot.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ran Arad","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUiL-s8WLKyIxSNVOIElBQRpC9Q675-SdP0Ghgv5EW3cZun-ALT=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"The music was much to loud, smoking was allowed everywhere, my ears are still ringing when I write this, and my hair smells of cigarettes. user_reviews: [{"Name":"Yara Jabali","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW3w2FBuLJqJ0OUtHftkd6jUWd_tRDSj8jr8dTnkP5ABXuaNPU=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Wow. I didn't think of writing anything here but after we got food poisoning I just had to. We were very disappointed with the food to say the least even before the food poisoning. Just look at the â€œchicken fingersâ€. Itâ€™s a frozen supermarket schnitzel!! Absolute disgrace. We really couldnâ€™t believe they served us that. And the nachos!! The toppings had no flavor and the nachos itself didnâ€™t taste good at all and I also believe itâ€™s supermarket bought. We also ordered a hamburger which was really average. We could barely eat anything and got out hungry and paid for garbage food. I guess when having such a big menu thats the food youâ€™re going to serve?! Itâ€™s best if you only serve drinks with no food at all. No wonder the place was empty. Other than that the music was good and the waitress was really nice. But we would not ever return to this place and would not recommend it.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMZ5HOe9aCacP_aBfYPXEdB6Z71w0xJq2sBsZQD\u0026fid=0x0:0x20be345000b7fcd9"],"When":"2023-8-1"},{"Name":"Marc Berry","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI5axmHLgPKqa51z3qIU7vY89SrcVzpSi802is5CSs48wc0cA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba8-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Liked it here, good staff, lots of screens, music and good quality food (like burgers etc). I went to watch the West Ham have last night, as one of the owners died earlier, and was happily watching and drinking, along with others, when some load mouth asked to change the channel to a different game, and was obliged. I wasn't happy, and this idiot then proceeded to shout during that game, and sing to whatever was being played.. addi we felt very uncomfortable and left.  There are plenty of screens to show different games on, to change all of them over was really quite rude.  Wouldve given 5 stars if it wasn't for that","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNCgvQUXOGpm7DJJ56L1l_oy6LEdvQNhxFMuXTu\u0026fid=0x0:0x20be345000b7fcd9"],"When":"2023-1-5"},{"Name":"Noel McGarrell","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWRxdq16DXnqHLWlDe-YzYQMtQPVut-bOjDWnUmCkiFwhffuCGUzg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Good selection of beers, including a Jerusalem Beer IPA which was different. Service was a bit inattentive - they seemed to spend a lot of time on their phones. Seen several potential pointers wait at the tables and then get up and leave. That was until a staff change over where it improved.\nThat said, it was nice watching the city go by while having a pint. There was also live music on the street, adding to the atmosphere.\nWeird hybrid between an English and Irish bar. However, more the former given how the Guinness was poured.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNkvxn8kly6BpEQ3QFfLmqI5v_sIisFKrzGL4R_\u0026fid=0x0:0x20be345000b7fcd9"],"When":"2023-10-4"},{"Name":"Lola Dadon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXoGOJ8sPdkRNFSZST7usZdjx_p-5ZG208Rx6Ujgkxr2DrtfFUhiw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The nicest place in the area. Laid back bar with an excellent menu that changes constantly. This is not the place for refined dining, but the food is very good and on par with a casual restaurant. You can definitely go there for a meal.  And they are open every day of the week.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMncsRV9tWRhV10JT27eEd3CR1OUflwHwKkPvKD\u0026fid=0x0:0xcbe18246ea4e47d0"],"When":"2022-6-18"},{"Name":"Mushi Merdler","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW2jhEZGp4Vep7ahIwxuRYLKv5feDLgN4nh2ALkQZHlxFL8vlU=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Real Tel Aviv atmosphere. Few dishes the eat by the beer but with a lot of thinking and great quality. Donâ€™t look for a fancy plating. Itâ€™s a truly Tel Avivian Bar","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Michael Olshansky","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXX61wd2boH8NVva-SQMZH9kDolVUM2Mh4GZQmKDkjjh_pkPgNVew=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Tel Aviv is very high paced with lots of places open and close all the time. Stands out the iconic Minzar, which never disappoints with excellent beer selection, best food you can wish for (in a pub) and awesome signature vibe. Opens early on and always busy with market goers, tourists and later on with loyal crowds to finish the night. This place is a must.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOluYsUCyPBw4EpVeyMAhKNpJae3NA37mv9JAyo\u0026fid=0x0:0xcbe18246ea4e47d0"],"When":"2019-8-10"},{"Name":"Uri Ar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUMThW2KLH_F1rIFhKX6XDcZyK0YuJ8j7scN7fNXbvvG6Yt8HY=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My favorite spot in Tel Aviv. [{"Name":"Rupert A.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLc1z9bLynhgKGkihxX-cpS9pSPodymkNd2IFPssLXm5QGQeA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Florentino is the "Soho" district of Tel Aviv.
This restaurant/bar represents the spirit of the neighborhood with funky, eclectic interior and a semi covered outdoor seating (with headlamps on cool days)

The server, Atalia, was amazing.  She is very friendly and efficient and really makes one feels welcomed.
ALL the food that we had was from their extensive VEGAN food choices of their menu.
We had a "chicken" schnitzel  cheeseburger, a burger made out of chestnuts and sweet potatoes, grilled eggplant with teaching sauce, veg salad.  The "eggs" that look taste and behave like real eggs were ALL VEGAN substitutes.
They also have a large selection of beers on tap and wines.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOkieX12orddAzLacNyphDnBOeddvJUZCLZReKM&fid=0x0:0x8c862d971193a562"],"When":"2022-3-13"},{"Name":"Kiariladyboss","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUCEIQq7u4XLgEzL_AKtN5X92ml-ugV3sa6GTf414nIAAMrrAQF3Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had dinner at Shuffle Bar and loved the food, the vibe and the service. They have many vegan options. I tries the Arais made of soy, it was delicious!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNqR5CP-qmXfsVJBH2KlmLCMF6pOWQWYX9QWzks&fid=0x0:0x8c862d971193a562"],"When":"2023-5-9"},{"Name":"Lia Ismailov","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIJ8VjLNFo7a5ln8VGSrTZLZM98PaPAd6KEDjYFKZtTuQj1ug=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I love the multiple vegan options and also the prices are very cheap but the quality is really good.
Also the board games are amazing twist to all the bars in tel aviv.
Definitely one of my favorite places!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPrzngUg5OYMofR9ozvWVYxyWktTCopPqw2p689&fid=0x0:0x8c862d971193a562"],"When":"2021-9-9"},{"Name":"Michal Elia Kamal","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWpk1-ym1eEAPTa1gfWENIxXft7j8u_rGmhMYnzFVBYAm4tI4E=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The food was nice, many good vegan options, the waiter that evening was super sweet and friendly, it was my first time with some friends from abroad and it was a good spot in Florentine neighborhood to take them to.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOLpVYNLVwxywjxKfYNF9Rvqce-HhQMXlYTg592&fid=0x0:0x8c862d971193a562"],"When":"2023-5-2"},{"Name":"Rachel Ginsberg","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUlqhPtLRoUrSNCNHJWJy0tH9_nsqeLVgqE_AWgVV8HYAQPgOO-Mw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very cute and laid back bar I really liked the music there. The staff were very accommodating and happy hour is very worth it .
Happy hour - is till20:00 and you  have 50%on the alcohol and 20%on the food","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPnpA5tHe8KtzaEsXEd6PjiYk3ts_m1dWzfbM7B&fid=0x0:0x8c862d971193a562"],"When":"2023-7-15"},{"Name":"Nasma Shwahde","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVkkO4SUuI3oLLpn9KaYcu9csVO0Wa2mWeRcV44K5Wlem5EIWlDFA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Great vibes and atmosphere, very welcoming! The food was okay but not that delicious. We ordered asado and a vegan burger.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"AntonKZ","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUmVwg2u1JAB77EgNKCYJltd39f73rIwBsS6Kw6BkgKdfEYYiNp=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I like this place a lot because it's warm inside but there are also heaters outside - very comfortable in winter. The pineapple pizza is amazing. Good selection of beers. Service is ok-ish, responsive but a bit slow.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNoPzMjLp525ch44UXKYOanHfhdDd1HeWbwI4D-&fid=0x0:0x8c862d971193a562"],"When":"2023-3-8"},{"Name":"Lior Weizman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXvf2aikafxw_uhbObffvjPwrDRbNx2yV0akITGnGNT-FNYnCMSCw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Great vegan food! Bravo chaps.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Michael Olshansky","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXX61wd2boH8NVva-SQMZH9kDolVUM2Mh4GZQmKDkjjh_pkPgNVew=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I am biased, but this is one of my favorites in Florentine. My friend loved it even more than I did!! Loved the domestic Israel beer and my friend loved the beer nuts.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNjKO9YAMpnQ0-NWAUbmYZ-rXXMBqs8VRTHuBlX&fid=0x0:0x8ef269bff3be5b4d"],"When":"2018-8-28"},{"Name":"Manor Zemer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWZ6ez8s5L-8b5z-rJSMSAPOfKVwT2m77e5XaYfRzfPkFFa7IOTNg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Perla Bar in Tel Aviv is a great place to grab a drink and relax with friends. The staff are all incredibly friendly and welcoming, and they always make sure to take good care of their customers. The selection of beer is impressive, with a wide variety of options to choose from. Whether you're in the mood for a classic lager or something more unique and craft, you're sure to find something you'll enjoy at Perla Bar. Overall, I highly recommend Perla Bar for anyone looking for a fun and welcoming place to grab a drink in Tel Aviv.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Frank Stiegler","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWU7iTIOqfYln2dAsoo5YDoLOKYd4Hb0lv3w5jgQ0gXeAbtX-vLzg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great variety of beer (my favorite is the Negev Oasis), good food, super-friendly service (in English, too). I ordered truffle toast that was delicious!
The prices were low because of happy hour dill so that is recommended to come at those hours.
The atmosphere is nice, gray music and people, there is also a dance bar inside which is more active at Thursday.
A great place to grab a drink and snacks with friends.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"GuyZa","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWqf9QNBbPnJ4Nz0CoE-uOfQrrfpzYC_51cxrh1btjK_AnmpLF1=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"It was a nice place to grab a drink before catching a show. Try something else.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Gilad Levy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVAT57Al0j_XfBq1C_VEVFSuGDEEIvV7FwA_g8ylSZRHE-fqW4Dpg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Great happy hour!

Inside the music is too loud, only good for people who don't enjoy any kind of conversation at all. Also, they think it's cool to waste thousands of papers every night throwing them to the people just to cause a shock effect. I think it's cheap, wasteful and bothering because it falls into your food and the already expensive drinks. The staff is not very friendly neither helpful but they are not unfriendly either. Having so many options in Tel Aviv, I don't see any reason to come back again.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jonathan Jutrem Cohen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLNHje9et4Hk8UAb1pQgMEjg3d9vTG3vgUnXdhSD4xzBjB3YA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing place with good music, good drinks for a good prize, especially in happy hour! And it's super central. Right next to Dizengoff center, so it's easy to continue your night to where ever you need to go. It's a place where you can meet both local Israelis or also international students or tourists! Highly recommended for anyone looking for a good time at a cool bar.","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Oded Kassirer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWBVFWcOaiMdQjfS3MGw6Uu6B6JnkcUxFKUJt_-LJhMZl_V51QJ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We started with the Artichoke and Labane appetizer and it was absolutely amazing! We then had the Lamb kebab: very very good. The lamb and chicken: good, the brioche was maybe a little too thick, and the hamburger, that was perfectly cooked and delicious. Great service, beautiful place inside and out. Highly recommended.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOIj6Dsjm7CO_bHsRdKuoeGNi2XbYuOkI17pwbH&fid=0x0:0x7e87db22a9af0fbb"],"When":"2022-12-14"},{"Name":"Brandon Jackiewicz","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXVf7zPhSKW4mU1iMsYzR_h-tg8BzvPJJTkUR8FzgDLNq-SlzxX=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Just like my stars suggest, this place has amazing food, service and atmosphere. If you're in Jaffa, and you're local or new, morning or all nighter, you will find good times, good food, and good company here. Give it a shot, eat something you haven't before, and trust me... you won't regret it. :)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMX1hzWiHKUXc_AuKHewGcX9FaXuWC_j7SCfcU9&fid=0x0:0x7e87db22a9af0fbb"],"When":"2023-7-4"},{"Name":"Michael Salaverry","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWboG-cAjDxAgnIMS-BkPV34_otrll_mM2Hw_qZOZWcLlumj6kTwA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great Jaffa party on a Saturday restaurant. They even had a live DJ playing 80s hits. The food was wonderful. We did send the kebab back to get cooked thoroughly, but they were very understanding and professional. Excellent host as well. Highly recommend","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOjUYCPYKWYG5pVlm2yuv16cZqNQ5Hl54YUYDow&fid=0x0:0x7e87db22a9af0fbb"],"When":"2023-4-29"},{"Name":"Jane Chung","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjURUWPRLP6iBmcwarcBdm2jOIHG1EqApmaiikQEL8Z9ueEMNFKYOg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The herb salad and ceviche were fantastic! Exactly what we were looking for our brunch. We also love the eggplant dish with the creamy garlicky sauce. The restaurant was kind enough and get us a chocolate mousse on the house. Very nice ambiance and lively atmosphere.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMorLVYWY5igYJqjgk7B7tdNSHduza_kbUvQuJh&fid=0x0:0x7e87db22a9af0fbb"],"When":"2022-5-22"},{"Name":"Cedric Martin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW--ZYvS6afHrouMBeMebdJQ22d56_9qN7aYKmC-Wf0gfNaGk5y=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Located in the Jaffa flea market, this charming restaurant is the perfect spot for a nice dinner with a whole lot of Middle Eastern specialities. The food is really good and the atmosphere around Raisa is great. Strongly recommended!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMjje1L0LLoRb7WeXDSg6EPp9A4B_X2QSFu6_L-&fid=0x0:0x7e87db22a9af0fbb"],"When":"2023-9-8"},{"Name":"Arie Rozichner","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWsiV5wYoIh-42Le67--Zpaqp7bWXRkKeSkFJxTrObEVQh12ujArQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Nice place with good atmosphere and typical Jaffa ambience. The food is OK. The service is nice, but sometimes slow.
Had Israeli breakfast - good, and Artichoke and Labneh salad - didn't really connected to it - almost no rocket leaves, too much onions and labneh and chips.
Good value for your money.
Recommended mainly for simple food lovers and getting Jaffa atmosphere.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNDswi1bq9vpdiliO1ce0liZMwaIoIkKGin12ub&fid=0x0:0x7e87db22a9af0fbb"],"When":"2023-3-24"},{"Name":"Sean Harris","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUxhpNxaW7QK7DA2RIwkmtUc3AK45tVorFuYznWmwjUbco6Q8_i=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Really tasty bread, dips and lamb pitas and cigars. For the price - amazing quality food. Really friendly and funny front of house staff. Great vibes sitting outside watching the world go by. Good music and not too loud so you can still speak comfortably.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPy6uOQDgCU_3ZOkiXffD04LVeXwWYV4r-7L5zT&fid=0x0:0x7e87db22a9af0fbb"],"When":"2023-5-6"},{"Name":"Vincent Vasina","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLbMV4fS3KmuNsAD6mPvk-f16_4C8bzBqtgW1N-fSa4tYGW9w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"All-around good restaurant! Great ambiance, friendly bartender (and great cocktails!), good dinner options. The service for seated dinner was slow, which is why I rated four stars - it took us a while to get drinks, even though the restaurant didnâ€™t seem that busy. Regardless, would definitely recommend Raisa and looking forward to returning!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM5FjEScS09p4sKoQY9XrPla3lJ54XRoMsJ7zdC&fid=0x0:0x7e87db22a9af0fbb"],"When":"2022-11-20"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Itay C.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJpuSfQh4txU0XjNyABG_cZ8dAGB7iCbxqpccBeeoUhmhUrOw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A hidden gem in the heart of Tel Aviv. Located inside The Norman hotel is a quality cocktail bar that serves dishes directly from the hotel's restaurant. No reservations needed and the place is always fairly empty, essentially one of Tel Aviv's best kept secrets.

The lokus fillet dish (grouper fish) was delicious, cocktails refreshing and well prepared. Bread pudding dessert was divine. Immaculate service, if a bit slow. Pricey, as one expects from a hotel restaurant.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPkJXZnHD_laegtfyEjxBMLhU78xmMPI9or39ct&fid=0x0:0x484fba9ba0573a21"],"When":"2019-9-18"},{"Name":"Yotam Kadishay","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVV3xsk5TmnUQ5kTHcBO9wVPuhyehttCaxLCuFvJ8AVngPlvbxpJw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Cocktails quality wise and service - itâ€™s a five.
But the overall vibe is more of a hotel-lobby-restaurant-waiting-library-waiting kinda place.
Meaning I wouldnâ€™t go spend a full night there, but as a gateway drug to dinnings or alena it is perfect.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPS0jCRned15QnrB4EyvpooV2eMKkRXjg1SlfHc&fid=0x0:0x484fba9ba0573a21"],"When":"2019-11-22"},{"Name":"Rebecca Brindza","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVecen_w3nMyiOEBOg9Q3zy8LFCL76e4MOqyQGAk6ovzcdc8Htg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Great spot in Tel Aviv for classic cocktails, fun fare, a 1920s vibe and spot on service. The bartenders make the best Vespers and dirty martinis in the city. You MUST try the octopus skewers cooked in lamb fat ğŸ¤¤.

The bar does not take reservations, you can however make a reservation at the restaurant, Alena. We love to stopping by for lunch or evening drinks!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP6qgg6C5HDus5AcpBPw-GyJpxNTW_JNpsaQv4W&fid=0x0:0x484fba9ba0573a21"],"When":"2021-7-9"},{"Name":"David Mor","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXUxuo5NFedyavYtAuhSS2_qQKMx6S9FpuaqgUaD2jAJ5_j8v_y=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Library Bar is a lovely aristocratic style bar with a great selection of cognac drinks and a really warm atmosphere. The food that comes from the hotel restaurant, Alena, is amazing but what really blew our mind was the staff. They were super nice and chatty and they even surprised us with an extra desert! An expensive place but worth it!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO0ABQtcgwwDAj2_Wq3mFYNTEhWJiX6e34BQfnK&fid=0x0:0x484fba9ba0573a21"],"When":"2019-2-16"},{"Name":"Yam Mesicka","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWDsHdzsTm1J3fqGcPRqEoWpSTpLOOoWiu9xn8hoeJrDlwTqtAn9Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Excellent atmosphere, great cocktails.
Beautiful and fancy place with average cocktail prices, where the service can be either great or disappointing.
Absolutely best Martini in Tel Aviv. Try to stick to the menu.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNG7QOFgfR2FssuTXF_eO4KYOqli2eXeG6HEWeq&fid=0x0:0x484fba9ba0573a21"],"When":"2019-6-17"},{"Name":"Danielle Abis","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVLgsfSAO8IbS_bBLDk5-v8qaNyUhbM2AF4GZm3TTAehxq4h63h=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Really liked the drinks and the staff was friendly. It's also a very intimate bar with sofa seating. It's a little pricey, but not too bad.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM-SabEYWOXmmmwQ56XT7_F0q7e4F-qsmhy1mQ&fid=0x0:0x484fba9ba0573a21"],"When":"2021-8-17"},{"Name":"Jonathan Ben Chanoch","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJEPF18weUaQHQJw2Brhdz1QpyHEfq_lYnDQJW5HIhIpM6oaA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"As many people here have already said, this is a hidden gem. One of the most aesthetically pleasing bars in Tel Aviv, you'll feel like you're in a different world when you walk in.

Fantastic cocktails, great food and that special atmosphere perfect for intimate meetings or a nice date. I'd say they serve the best Vesper Martini in the city.

They do not take reservations beforehand, so I suggest showing early-ish (19:00/20:00) to make sure you have seating. If you do decide to come later you may have to wait a bit for a spot, especially during the weekends.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lev Kantor","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXefIRBC7cddrRJnxaxg7Rt8FHBMyrk_awtJ4hrJu3xZ7jWNb7XCg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing bar, great cocktails. Yonatan is the best barmen ever","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMQyuz90-egDdiDedH_igabz-jrKUCO55t8VQai&fid=0x0:0x484fba9ba0573a21"],"When":"2021-11-28"}]

[{"Name":"Adir Amidi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWq06JUvC2vRGwRSwdr3E53QLIWWI1XM_W-Ver7MUEGYGK7BqhXqw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Heard about this restaurant from a friend of mine, went there to check what's the hype is all about.
ordered the double burger and got the best experience I could ever dream of.
Definitely gonna recommend!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMqZpXAW2aDHJNZfxC94ywT3Y8_ocQb6YnF-ylu&fid=0x0:0x33d8b99859767529"],"When":"2021-9-12"},{"Name":"Valeria Z","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUiJVZyPVR0OXnJfCGeDiKTZtRYs8_O9KiaLdRcoEfPEM2wBy7WIQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The place itself is nice.
The view there is wonderful straight to the marina, boats and sea. Although they can improve their design and cleaning.
The food it's okay I ordered fish and chips, they have option to add cheese on the chips that wasğŸ”¥  tasty ğŸ˜‹
They don't have decent vegetarian options.
What it's really good about this place are their cocktails, if you are looking for a place for drink and enjoy a nice evening this is your first option in Ashkelon.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"ilan bondar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVzQagcFRYQ8Zoh-D3mekOJ7ZUZAmPwIwkkGqyGTsTP-7loHb-R=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The waiters & bartenders are warm and fun people, the music is great and the views are beautiful ğŸ˜","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNdIPqcxTMLkPt-izC2nAHV_iApBEm_4ko7Cb_v&fid=0x0:0x33d8b99859767529"],"When":"2023-8-24"},{"Name":"Shira Rabinowitz","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocID5elv1k6hPlk1JR8R5LYeFhU2gApau9LCUk7RLYq6QqXdxw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The best food and my new favorite restaurant. The mac and cheese, the pizzas, the bread and dips just wow. I've tried almost everything on the menu and each dish does not disappoint. Delicious taste and looks beautiful. Highly recommend.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Anna Frishman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVt4ibt5kANtiUYnvUtwIwx1nx6nlfoLemIdhisXe3MQ47zMNY=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We were waiting for pizza more then 20 min.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Scott Feucht","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUwEf9Q3Rhnp7jSpDzbilK0EQpU1aKa5XeqnJLIzpW0D3fI8SI=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Tried this restaurant tonight. I ordered the double burger with cheese and lamb bacon and my wife ordered a salad. The burger was over cooked (I ordered it medium well) and the bun was a soggy mess. My wife's salad was drenched in dressing and a soggy mess also. Thier alcohol selection is very basic and not a place to hang out for drinks. We were very disapointed in this place and don't plan to return. There are way better places on the boardwalk and beach area for dinner and drinks.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Chris Marsden","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLNoQCRIDlCc1mK3RRzyfXa0YBgql5ozaaf-fqzcF_qGXorGQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Been here a few times now & love this this place ! The staff are very friendly & welcoming, the food is amazing & the cocktails are to die for!! The atmosphere is great and you get a beautiful view of the marina, would definitely recommend ğŸ‘Œ","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Shawn Hayden","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV0SdqlTeoQtm9AlnDXOSqdN1AlIU8aA5CUEyvfxC8QmpC_wLk6=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Wow, really good music, grsat food, and very good service overlooking the sea. Had a great time with family.","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Elyasaf Jehuda","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJFWlpwXblcN0PE4PVxxfrBYSwbmz7SlyadzUaUv2TPUMdTcQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Awesome place!

Location is amazing on the beach.

You have many places to sit - outside where its quieter, inside but to the side where its louder but still can talk, or right infront of the stage and enjoy the shows!

My date took me there on a thursday where they had a live band playing which was amazing.

Customer service was great.

Will definitely come again!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNEuyIh4nh2C_NyV9o5kONtrpE7e9Na8GZTmvou&fid=0x0:0x795758f0c8ce7446"],"When":"2022-11-19"},{"Name":"maxmillian kagere","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXemNBVR2lNxC-yb3MhmYw2PsO9TX9T52_kQZE42crRpKXpoj9b=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"is a place at the entrance to beach ğŸ– there is a different music flavor different delicious foods drinks all day of the week is very good for the enjoyment, refreshing and relaxing ğŸ˜","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMZlIv4as1f601_8tWGPSbkJz0c-WJM1_13vhDm&fid=0x0:0x795758f0c8ce7446"],"When":"2022-7-8"},{"Name":"Nikita Nakonechnyi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVrsRY1FF5eAo6X6QuQTP6ExgKWr7C-q65RJ04dQ8FQRvknAv-O=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"There are not so many places in Israel with a good music. This is a rare one. Pleasant bar with a happy hours from 5 - 9 pm.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOtzKsbs8jlFK-ARqcVsJ5-fM9mz_25B0tpNgx5&fid=0x0:0x795758f0c8ce7446"],"When":"2020-6-12"},{"Name":"Adir Traitel","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVEYaBnpTP8uA7Drq6J57iwJ1njNUVdhV4uYt25UG_TD9sk-4e6Tg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Awesome location near the Mediterranean with the best possible view. Great food and the best alcohol your money can buy. Good music and atmosphere.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPIikme6k1g-2Iv_utP7fpDFGuiu7u2BJUq2_Zp&fid=0x0:0x795758f0c8ce7446"],"When":"2018-3-26"},{"Name":"Dennis Joeken","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXaIG-9UK35_QMKJ0PI4NJHr7dfcNfSMGpn_MT_a4Rwl5WHhGSI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I had "The Jack" Burger. It was tasty. Service was also great. There was only one super loud drunk lady at the bar. The staff told her multiple times to be quite, which did not really help. But oh well. It is how it is :-) we still enjoyed the evening.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nir Vaknin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIio8utBLJxRW81FlFZChUrKP3yUeHa4pmPYq3HoFk9p50xJQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"very nice place good vibe good music
great burger","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNNW6GcMgqnKgID1E77U893nIFpQZ75Tiy_ATew&fid=0x0:0x795758f0c8ce7446"],"When":"2021-6-10"},{"Name":"Nicole","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJbQYPKxVoHVWTOFcESaElfKb2JVIW2ZWdDH5xpXEE3IC6SpfI=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The best place I were at.
fair prices, waiters are funny and polite, I didn't have to wait long. the music is amazing, drinks were good and food was great!
definitely will come back again","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Herman Sodokolov","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJTMYrI_bBdY0HC7IEhNe1CdGg4awVZGL1E17OqRAueHqxRGA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Allround terrible experience!!

Went there to eat after reading a lot of misleading reviews.

The place was dirty, the staff was completely disinterested and the food was absolute garbage!

We ordered 1 pizza to share. The menu said 'thin crust pizza baked in a wood oven' Sounds promising right?  What we got was a tortilla (an actual tortilla!!!!) with some cheap garbage yellow cheese and hardly any toppings, baked in a toaster oven! To ad insult to injury, we had to pay extra for the toppings. I seriously had better food on airplanes.

We paid close to 100 Shekel for 1 tortilla "pizza" and two soft drinks (no alcohol). I would say this is not even a low quality experience, but in my opinion more an actual rip off.

To make things worse, the tables were sticky, the place smelled like vomit and stale beer and they allow other guests to smoke inside where people eat.

I felt dirty, cheated and ripped off after the experience and I got the impression that's exactly what they intent to do. I think The Jack is an embarrassment for Ashkelon and they're giving the city a bad name.","Images":null,"When":""}]

There's a daily happy hour (even on Friday!) and some decent food options at prices lower than in Tel Aviv. The music was to my liking and the service was good.
Lowering the stars only because they allow people to smoke inside, seriously? Getting home stinking from cigarettes is not something I missed at all.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sergei Plahotia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWc6nTlqS_4jKQNW09d5OqEgV-XzBIuHNmWpx-9mRpsCqsVj6M=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Nice and cozy pub. However, they allow smoking inside the pub.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Guy Khalat","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJFvRx6IT5zv8AOtj_MPOkoVpqL12YnmA2yTC-288g8lotrAw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Really Fun Little bar, great food, great atmosphere.
They have SpongeBob on TV!
One of my favorite places!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Uzi Cohen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV_-Qnz1F5gG5HvWWmuJ0cYphzBQxH98Z3JO972_XR37DBc3tFC=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"A very neighborhood bar. it's cozy and small (sometimes too small).The prices are quite cheap and general atmosphere is good. You can find people from all ages and the music is mostly old classic rock. The only disadvantage is the fact that the place is REALLY small, so on weekends you can wait quite a few time outside untill you get a table.

[{"Name":"Yishay Yovel","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVaEZHOm_aSJKjjiA8Ggq-rsAXmd2oAfLJNmbc1IVqGLtxYvJaHlQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is one of the best restaurants in Israel. The menu was intriguing and the food was amazingly executed. The flow and pace of the meal was just right and the service (thanks, Niki) was knowledgeable and pleasant. The meal is expensive, basically what you would expect in a Michelin star restaurant. It should get one.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Emanuel Rosenzweig","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXHEtyWTSJdlcICnd8GjGKdjdHaNRtCInfdFQPGNNUMyL5NUIy0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"One of the best restaurants in Israel. Every single dish has its own unique interpretation and style. Clever play with flavors and textures.
The service is professional and the overall experience is fantastic.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMTGhZGtJJ_npATfjqKPXBuxx58rRUvfpcGnSik&fid=0x0:0xd72f878298a9af5d"],"When":"2023-5-21"},{"Name":"Kris T","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX3_tCK-Xbxvwi7N_hWz2mAcoaAIkny1d9vDhcl74Bug6Fn0VpSJA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I heard so much about this restaurant and expected more. Waiters were getting the orders wrong and forgetting things; food was expensive and meat was great but some of the other dishes and deserts were average. Sea tartar was so full of coriander that killed all other taste, and it was not even mentioned in the ingredients. Atmosphere was ok but also more on the basic side. Lack of attention to details or creating exclusive experience.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOin-CavBzuM9MuK95763H7uxYpK6ZqsVwIqVhV&fid=0x0:0xd72f878298a9af5d"],"When":"2023-9-20"},{"Name":"Alex Okin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIONNgRLxqCFEuNgE8MgvvtzFokpgoZmiJIz7ekT1zGkmaflg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Starting with the service, we were served by Nikki who was exceptional. Explained everything to the last detail, and took care of everything we needed. The food was incredible, unique combinations and flavor bombs. Honestly I don't have a specific recommendation, just order a couple of each section. This was a great experience and we will definitely come back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPvHKuTBob2NOCkJ2eEi-Cu38PMAdMyeDUbzN-c&fid=0x0:0xd72f878298a9af5d"],"When":"2023-7-21"},{"Name":"Mai Srugo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKBddj7_zQu_3wyy4y4YYMelHs5mnekghXCvOTw_eF4dHyx7A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"One of the city's absolute gems!
Entering through the boutique Hotel Drisco, you're immediately transported to a Parisian-like ambiance. The dining experience here is exceptional, with every bite feeling like a dream.
I highly recommend trying their gnocchi, which is like fluffy clouds, and their lobster pasta. The atmosphere is truly unique, adding to the overall amazing experience.
It's worth noting that the prices are on the higher side, but the exceptional quality justifies it.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMs56ZDHRayXwRx1a2EwCnfSS6Ouk-cNvh5qdgb&fid=0x0:0xd72f878298a9af5d"],"When":"2023-8-21"},{"Name":"Yael Shenhav","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWLPMeB1uP-Azs3EnfgzmtDCXLB431LQADyOKG0uDiEongAE1g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Good fine dining restaurant - some interesting dishes , Mediterranean flavors , lots of fish dishes and good service . Only downside is one of the specials was a Rascasse fish - full of fish bones for only few bytes of fish . Prices are high - not unlike similar restaurants in Tel Aviv","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMPHZa3YJHbxLeL6vcjGeHdhzEghhswB4R7Szt7&fid=0x0:0xd72f878298a9af5d"],"When":"2023-8-15"},{"Name":"Leeju Singh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWqao1CBoep44_FnGR8xITCm928QEps6jD5-3n4X0MREayY7MSO=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have been trying chef restaurants in tel Aviv, from time to time.  George and John has very nice service and food is just delicious.  I would highly recommend if you guys are looking for delicious and unique combination. Ofcourse the price are higher then normal restaurants with small portion but trust me you would not regret by spending money there. ğŸ˜Š","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMyOrh4scp9cuFY6GN1Ur3o1CgxsoT-Ky4f3C4&fid=0x0:0xd72f878298a9af5d"],"When":"2023-9-7"},{"Name":"Tal Lichtenstein","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWSiGfsuYyLIaJubz7R0pJhj1CwIB3DOmWZQOVeSMdyhiL_oq8Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"We visited for breakfast. The good - everything was very tasty and fresh. The disappointing - the variety has dropped considerably since our visit about a year ago: Breakfast now consists of a main dish (omelette, bedict, etc), six tiny dishes of fish/cheese/spread samples that are not refilled, and a buffet that has a veg. salad, spreads, butter and bread/pastries. Everything was of high quality, but we would have expected some more for the price they charge. There are definitely better options in the area.","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Vasil Khachiashvili","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXDop7ADn65OKesSnE6fah_UfbslSyP2WKvwgyw-NP2NgTDVZd2MA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great place !!! Great food, good music !!!
Most Delicious FISH AND CHOPS Ever !!!!
I Have tried it at many places around the world here they are the best!!! And also SHRIMPS in cream and garlic souce are amazing !!! YOU SHOULD TRY !!!

Edit: They Renewed Menu, and again its awesome !!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPeUE2kJQY4MfxQ4XOjADagmUlYLodejYBytwhX&fid=0x0:0x1a970b27ff9b84c7"],"When":"2018-12-7"},{"Name":"Samuel Samuelson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUAUD7Mv8-xUd6gcM2_CzZXtwQjTyuG_RWvGV8GNx18KQhzUMZ4CA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is hands down the best place to hang out in Ashkelon. Sitting right on the beach gives it a great relaxed vibe during the day, and at night it livens up with loud music for a younger crowd. Great food (that's not just limited to appetizers) is sure to please, but a wide selection of beer and liquor sets it apart from even the best restaurants in Israel. Whether you're looking for a family friendly place to eat lunch, or a raucous bar to burn the midnight oil, Archie's Public House does not disappoint.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOpppyIRWK1P1T1NyKFvIaVmUgvjB_NLwxIv2fD&fid=0x0:0x1a970b27ff9b84c7"],"When":"2017-1-27"},{"Name":"Elchin Abdullayev","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXdxdmcsDFXEEvoKPqTNaEAmCxzo0YZvKxxmH3p1ymO9astoh4J=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Maybe one of the best pub-style restaurants in Ashkelon. Eqplant was great as was fish & chips. Perfect fast service, nice people. Next to the beach.
5* all around.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOSZ2KIuDaeBqEoFHw-azHSoB9WVwl5SaIBgHoo&fid=0x0:0x1a970b27ff9b84c7"],"When":"2023-4-11"},{"Name":"David Kliger","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLSYa7IkE8WK_f9fEXJxqCVRDV2J0fJid5M1Iuqu2U_uDfeAA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great place!!!
Superb atmosphere, lovely service and the food was delicious.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNtL_Ay9ci5mwHJNS4u1zvUGwdWaG7gpf87Fbnu&fid=0x0:0x1a970b27ff9b84c7"],"When":"2023-2-17"},{"Name":"Ron Breger","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWi1PvL1F-2_INDwEHu0eRXNNpj869-Z87VkfpJNgPu-rgA220mSw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great place with great food. [{"Name":"Or Rochlin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV0YBwdznWqgmMI6rzYUua-ajTJRwnKhqZojQ4P6vOpO8I9vb4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Magdalena! One of the best restaurant in the Galilee. Modern cuisine with local Arab touch. The restaurant is very beautiful and the atmosphere is very peaceful. The service is excellent and the food is so delicious! ;)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPY1cpfk724SEoYxoJDQJtpwDoavwsV_MZs-D4&fid=0x0:0xb9a103aabe9f3e0"],"When":"2023-4-5"},{"Name":"Ami Giz Guided Tours","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVCFpPPQJPodlzCRRbz9kXyHFOM5igB_KmMJx4K7DTFwr2zwele_Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My favorite restaurant by the Sea Of Galilee .
As an Israeli Tour Guide i love it and always bring my tourists here ,try and share large variety of dishes.
Enjoy!!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNRfzlvYSWe-X-H2kQnASbOmt9SpktZuoVr9dV7&fid=0x0:0xb9a103aabe9f3e0"],"When":"2022-12-6"},{"Name":"Roy Latke","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUibr29cj0e-T6n24qKODTYwbdPVIN7L6f7NPALV9YmuKG1rKsAGA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My 3rd time here and itâ€™s always a win. Variety of amazing dishes. If you're with a group, consider get all the first dishes and share them","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPnk9BQ8uzJvU3XG9SlZdkrdaq8crlME9ry2m4Q&fid=0x0:0xb9a103aabe9f3e0"],"When":"2023-7-20"},{"Name":"Ronny On","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU6u8sBC-9dLuJitjwXB4wuwg4cMGtERSxlI1WcL6gnuDRNlHDV=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"One is the best restaurants in the area!
Their dishes are original and always delicious, with a huge variety of amazing first courses.
The service is as professional as it gets, friendly and attentive to your needs and special requests.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMWWZoL2BddMSxeKWbLbpMEJknl3Z4ZUCDJhqD2&fid=0x0:0xb9a103aabe9f3e0"],"When":"2023-4-9"},{"Name":"Yuval K","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWMhu_BtuT6xVPhpaH-uRPhJ82PKXuXCxJ17XcBQ8qilTX6ZFWrLg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Fabulous! It all starts with excellent service. From our own waitress and others. Pleasant service yet knowledgeable and not pushy. Then comes the delicious food. We had 12 dishes in total. The firsts were all great. The arais, the mushrooms, the goose liver and others all fantastic. We had two main dishes. The lamb chops are amazing. The fish less. From the desserts we loved the katayef with is fried dough with nuts and other good things. Beautiful restaurant and great food and service. It's a must!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPPolPZ3h7ARtSpHyK43TGgLEWt1wQkSdGvuVz3&fid=0x0:0xb9a103aabe9f3e0"],"When":"2022-8-15"},{"Name":"Shame A Name","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX6ovtiiDllWWnf5Z7F9T06lTsE3OfoYT8LgQbQ0GRbfiGeVgGN=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had lunch here on the way to River Jordan from Capernaum. The food is of very good quality. The fish was fresh and the lamb meat was well seasoned and properly cooked that it remains juicy. Staff were helpful and our main meals were served altogether as you would expect in a premium restaurant.  We spent 2 hours here as we enjoyed the setting and the view.  In terms of price, you would expect to pay a bit more considering the area and the ambience this restaurant provides.  We had a fantastic meal.  The restaurant is located on the upper floor, lift on site.  The toilets were clean in keeping with the premium feel.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPgBYEXqO2EXqWRoBU5X6JRnxeQTVMWx9ylMS0M&fid=0x0:0xb9a103aabe9f3e0"],"When":"2019-11-4"},{"Name":"Itzik levy (Izikl)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUMhOPtKPne5dwZdLYeB-7gSBitO9rV3432q_evRYLwaOfT2JvsFw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba8-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Chef's Restaurant.  Restaurant in front of it on Route 90. Reservations are required in advance, especially on weekends.  The service is excellent.  Beautiful and special dishes.  Istanbul sticks, cigars stuffed with cheese.  Lamb chops, amazing.  Excellent borta salad, tomato pieces and mozzarella.  Very expensive prices","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMgBc9UEuPbuezLN5eivdFWr9tnlIj2Qq12G5gV&fid=0x0:0xb9a103aabe9f3e0"],"When":"2023-8-6"},{"Name":"Haim Molcho","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX7cgN3oNbwgHSAT05ArPhZ-ZSASMM0ZwRKJ7M9Ju9VLKZSJM8HXw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Excellent restaurant with excellent service. The first courses are very tasty and special, quite large to share. The main courses may be less unique, but tasty and large. Our waiter was eager to help with vegan dishes.
The desserts are unusual, especially the â€œMalabi cannoliâ€ and â€œLebanese nightsâ€.
The price is reasonable in relation to the quality and quantity.
Weâ€™ll be back!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOGCrx46lpLX2yI16uIu1Dj_w2sVNJ3L5SaxZPT&fid=0x0:0xb9a103aabe9f3e0"],"When":"2022-6-24"}]

[{"Name":"Maor Alkobi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIiw29AVvFkWWLUbXe9u1VnZnz5A2PzY2Yua9SGbZnBeTpsEA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"The vibe and drinks was great! So is the hookah and the location is amazing (beach front), I wouldnâ€™t order any food there as it tasted much like bar food, I would give the food 1/10. The service is not great but thatâ€™s what happens when you include service as part of the check, the waiters really donâ€™t care about customers.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMZULxDogiL6N75ZMU4zIukWBTcdyni2PfSwFHO&fid=0x0:0x1a0f020f1e1670d1"],"When":"2022-10-13"},{"Name":"Yaron Shemesh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVmh7cDE4nAQOeOrzMs-KuHFHfsdoPVDN2Sx79Yqyk_ipwLph5VuA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The service was OK. The food was OK. We waited for sometime to get the check but was told some people were in shift about 15 hours so understand (not sure this is ok from labor point...). The service of 10% (usually I leave more than 15%), was already included in the bill mentioned there as optional but this fact was never mentioned by the them when charged my credit card. I almost doubled my tip.
Bottom line,  food and place location are OK, cost is reasonable. Make sure to review the check and see that tip is included so not leave double.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMOJaotvM1hMBclEQJUwDD5la_vLC2m0UcYGnx6&fid=0x0:0x1a0f020f1e1670d1"],"When":"2021-8-9"},{"Name":"Larytet.android Larytet","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKey9-XNJ0HTkU4mz5KqSKyIEnxJ7gPuRO7__wlGkjzbDsfCA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Petra in Ashdod is a place where the setting truly shines. With its prime location right by the sea, youâ€™re treated to a beautiful evening sun descending over the waterâ€”an ambiance thatâ€™s hard to beat. The menu is a sprawling 15 pages long, full of vibrant imagesâ€”a culinary tour for those who canâ€™t decide on just one destination.

As for the food, itâ€™s decent. There are certainly better, hmmm,  culinary experiences to be found in Tel Aviv, and yes, some might find a few dishes a bit on the, for missing a  better word, simple side. However, itâ€™s unlikely youâ€™ll leave dissatisfied. Even my kids, who consider themselves in, despite a few grumbles, were quietly focused on their meals for a good 20 minutes.

In the end, Petra offers a well-rounded experience. The view, and the atmosphere ensure a pleasant evening out. Itâ€™s an experience that leaves me feeling that less than 5 stars wouldnâ€™t do it justice.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nina Strelets","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIDzoH18VpyecJKWJlDxFtGMA9GrJJVF0oHUdYTajvgY8gNJQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Petra in Ashdod offers a decent dining experience with a lovely view of the sea. While the food is satisfactory, the real highlight is the scenic backdrop. A solid choice if you're looking to enjoy a meal with a beautiful view. By the way, they automatically charge 10% tip for the service. Total rating: 3.6/5 .","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Alina Gurevich","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJJxY7xgSTZ1cx1oZRchCSpqEHb98Nml2B0b3FOHbjQMyKbmg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"We made same day reservation for this place to celebrate my birthday with a family. It was Friday evening. However,  when we arrived nobody could find our names on the reservation list. It was very busy with big line of people trying to get in. And very loud music.  Thankfully we had saved recorded audio of making reservations and finally we were sitted. We told about my birthday when reservation been made and also right away to our waitress.  I saw other people celebrating with waitstaff bringing them desert with sparklers and singing for them.  It looked like fun and I was expecting to have the same. We ordered food and were waiting for at least some glasses for water. Food was good,  portions are huge. We ordered khachapuri among the other dishes,  but it didn't arrive till almost the end of our dinner.  We thought it was forgotten and it would be OK, since we were full already,  but it arrived by the end. During the dinner we were hunting for waitstaff,  since nobody came to check on us. Another waiter came by and we again asked for a birthday special.  We ordered desert only for this reason.  And when another waiter brought desert, he just put it on the table and left.  No birthday song , no sparkle,  no nothing. I was so upset. And at same time we saw someone else is celebrating properly.  Finally our waitress showed up to bring our bill. We told her what happened,  she just looked surprised,  turned around and left. No apology at all, no care. I wouldn't even tip her, but tips already included in bill. We were so disappointed. I feel upset even 2 days later.  Very bad experience.  We won't come back!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"George Mack","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIom1q9dFpBY_paUNMh2iAuxMhVYBbU2sLOB5nTHTg6eCjYyg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Fantastic views across the Mediterranean. Wonderful big breakfast and halloumi cheese filled calamari. Must visit.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPdZq0N3d7zeKqgeCXAvtwkIsZYR5vy4oaNxEoe&fid=0x0:0x1a0f020f1e1670d1"],"When":"2023-10-5"},{"Name":"David Feldman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ8BH6O7EpD2tADa5qwE-dS-1J0sOxSGWEZ3lfylHYN8dedoA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"My 3rd visit in two years. Overall I like the place and the food. The traditional Georgian dishes are great. Not cheap but portions are huge (share).","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPhwSEyV5_prks072sKt6ZcMEZrktJpUXFomEa2&fid=0x0:0x1a0f020f1e1670d1"],"When":"2018-12-22"},{"Name":"Vasil Khachiashvili","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXDop7ADn65OKesSnE6fah_UfbslSyP2WKvwgyw-NP2NgTDVZd2MA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This place is full with very delicious Georgian food.
EXCEPTIONAL IS KHACHAPURI - Even in Georgia You can hardly find like that and deffinitely - The best Megruli Khachapuri in israel !!! Bravo !!! I LL BE BACK !!!

[{"Name":"Robert Amery","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXedqaZD1FZmIQjejnSRrvOLmgGuR_n0LL9KzrPXx4YcYTDZ57t=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very nice restaurant,  kosher dairy and very tasty. Easy big car park and the restaurant we had to book ahead. We took the thai mix platter for 1st course, and an assortment of fish from the menu for our main course, and finally coconut ice cream, cream boulle and Ratatui ice cream.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOXvX98apa3c3ktBy5kHcoj0cPvSeEO7hOd1iu5&fid=0x0:0x7c308351dc704c03"],"When":"2022-5-1"},{"Name":"Galit Cohen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX5s26EYzun46Y2UbZvhRjWxS6ecH24U5FkKkLRy5AIiAuG8O-N=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Food was excellent, service quick.
One thing which I didn't like, we had to sit in a table for four, when we are five.
When I asked the waitress to add a table , she said you will manage....and refused to add a table.
The food was packed plate over plate, for the amount of money we paid it felt wrong,
Sitting in a fancy restaurant and eating like you sitting In a cheap dinner..","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNt71eC6nrUWskEp_pa2NrIKR5gyRQGpvjRxVFc&fid=0x0:0x7c308351dc704c03"],"When":"2022-5-10"},{"Name":"Shalev Moyal","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL596dMJWmXKqvSg9wKsajiG_A6Qhse0WYe25XqSGvMTaZ4gEwh=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Wonderful place! Everything is delicious and looks so good. The place itself is beautiful and quite fancy. The service is just great. Dishes are saved in no time. Very recommended!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPaN5Ntjf5r-S75NazxamKeYgdfOryERjvxRqxa&fid=0x0:0x7c308351dc704c03"],"When":"2019-3-23"},{"Name":"Eitan Hajaj","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL302Fx_R5aYY-uEhBZyK5ESdqvA41naUoE2p6snwm00NcAeA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great food and service.
The place look great,
We came 13 people and really enjoyed our time there.
The dishes are big and not too expensive.
Very recommended, also it's kosher place.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMVIGteCCBrlv-n5szKKu-sxkkKbtwg8LsmWe8T&fid=0x0:0x7c308351dc704c03"],"When":"2020-1-24"},{"Name":"Ronny van den Bergh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV9g30xjQ-mf5Ue6NNvJ6rxvAiYFaDQ-oMapu0xS6DpCIOcXb-1=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Very nice food, but be aware the portions are huge. The garlic focaccia was delicious
Great service","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO04elG-zli9aoafdZ8hxjIOh9F2I0B-Mw4OWIW&fid=0x0:0x7c308351dc704c03"],"When":"2022-5-20"},{"Name":"C E","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIvqCRMusPRjIlBbPUaWYxlWOjhzmsY0fod6P1vKjIkRnepUg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I went on my birthday at this â€˜â€™famousâ€™â€™ restaurant that actually it was not what I expected.
Food it was average, same as in a pub or a night club.
The smell of the place was horrible, smell of toilet in all the restaurant.
They tried to put some spray but didnâ€™t solve the issue.
Pasta was ok, but very expensive price.
The waiter was nice.
The place himself looks old and the plates could be more nice for this â€˜â€™fancyâ€™â€™place.
I felt like I am eating in some friendâ€™s home, nothing special.
The garden of the restaurant it is nice.
I will never come back to this place and not send any people to it.
Itâ€™s an average place where you can spend time with family but in high prices.
You can really feel you are in a village.
Very disappointed.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Steven King","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWkhrgRGnxe3Ir4zemEodlwp-Piacy9bcfRcrWNVcgUwU4PM9Y8uw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Worst meal , presentation awful , service awful
Asked for a hot piece of fish and hot mash potato ,
Was served cold
When I complained it took 15 min of running around to make it right by that time was too late , was offered a plate of dessert that looked like a mess for compensation. Big let down as drove long way to visit this restaurant. 1/10 overall","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Miriam Abrams (Deals Seeker)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWpCI6M4smJet0N4YQALPUeZhisQnWj6yPX3n_ktW_KfQ9J83fK=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Stunning surroundings and atmosphere. I had an Israeli breakfast and the vegetables were absolutely delicious, so fresh everything was perfect, a very special place. And wonderful service. If you want to go to a unique place for a special occasion, this place is it for dairy, or Space for meaty.","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews: [{"Name":"Nicole G","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/local-reviews/AJMZ0QeNj0UTN0yIrCGyJ0JhWwDODOg5QjAH0gdfB9Ji-oFl0zWFI-YVmhNAr-FGLycdpIjFmw=s120-c-br100","Rating":0,"Description":"Pina Barosh was wonderful.  I stayed there with my mother and my aunt. Nili made us feel completely at home, and could not have been more welcoming.  The location was perfect for touring the Galilee region,and the view from the hotel is beautiful.  The rooms were comfortable and unique.  Breakfast was delicious.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Brett O","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/local-reviews/AJMZ0QfHhPp0vyvo1Wo3WY4NH1G5QOPAHGBMv_XiebXLZtHzVwVa3wkRhb3dykyKrUCZPlawDA=s120-c-br100","Rating":0,"Description":"Beautiful location with sweeping view of the valley from the dining area. Has the character of a very old building with all the modern needs. The manager is extremely pleasant and goes  to any length to make your stay wonderful. We needed some glasses to have drinks with our friends and she meticulously cleaned and wiped each glass. Property is beautiful with many nooks for quiet reflection.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Avi Kessler","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJCutlsrJMh9RcUhQlGIQg6vbquaBs-dmLDzfVV3c8pgSSCWQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"There is Rosh Pina before Corona and Rosh Pina after Corona. Rosh Pina has still not recovered from Corona. There used to be places open in the evening serving a nice dinner. No more, maybe a truck if you are lucky. Pina baRosh was once one of those great establishments that ppl used to come a long way for. I would fly up here to eat breakfast in this place and then fly back to Tel-Aviv.\nI drove up here with the wife this time to be at a wine festival in Ramot Naftaly. Breakfast was ok. Service left much to be desired. This is true in many places in Israel. The view however from this place is still to die for. Give it a shot...","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMEDad8eHUqBD2OX6BC97taqbZh7hhaR-gAad84\u0026fid=0x0:0x13396909d82c2eff"],"When":"2023-6-6"},{"Name":"Udi Cohen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWwozTD9HNjYLj2MpsBYuwchPV4HcHW6C9dZrpt-1NkqUVq-NBs2w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The service with a smile and the readiness to assist is the great hallmark of this lovely , pleasant place.The rooms/ suites are comfortable albeit a bit old and it is evident that some update need to take place.Nevertheless ,the court that all rooms are facing, the garden and specially SHIRI BISTRO, the establishment's restaurant , make up big time for the rooms' lack of up to date feel.Still, the places ooze character  and if you haven't been there before, don't miss the vue from the garden or the restaurant- simply amazing, specially mount Hermon to the north, covered with snow in winter.Breakfast should be mentioned as a big highlight, tasty and wonderful experience.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"anne b","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/local-reviews/AJMZ0QdrOaBwvzVCVZGa_JCxmRob18-RTGR2NAc2ehM2ioIFQuUJBtaO6jr7GHqX15LV00VYsw=s120-c-br100","Rating":0,"Description":"My husband and I had been looking forward to staying at Pina Barosh for several years (pandemic put it all on hold for awhile) and it was worth the wait when we finally arrived last month for a 3 night stay. You don't get more friendly, welcoming and helpful than Merom, who greeted us when we walked into the informal check in area. ||||We had heard about Pina Barosh from others who had stayed there and it was everything we expected and more. Beautiful stone rooms and garden areas, photo-worthy and delicious breakfasts, a friendly staff, great music selections from a speaker on the terrace and the terrace itself where meals were served. Since dinner isn't served here since the pandemic, we just loved hanging out at the peaceful terrace at night listening to the music, looking out at the lights towards the Golan. ||||The bed and breakfast is located across from the Baron's Garden and the old city is a short walk uphill. We absolutely loved this place.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Janet K","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/local-reviews/AJMZ0Qdx0CtChWdL4amzhVtedU6JgNzs3A9KzPS8K998c7-u-mDeTb-7WQwuTD-PPX6BcVA5wg=s120-c-br100","Rating":0,"Description":"This was one of the most pleasant stays Iâ€™ve had in a Bed and Breakfast! The stone walkways, flowers and just atmospheric is wonderful. The views are amazing. I encourage you to try to get the deluxe suite. They gave us a lovely basket for breakfast along with made to order eggs and there was enough to pack for a picnic lunch! We didnâ€™t see much staff and I would suggest to management to circle around occasionally and when they do, they should speak to guests or at least nod! I think it will just take time for business as usual after COVID. I would recommend staying here and we will be back for sure!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Miryam Elisheva Honigman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVRNgeW_i0m4IO2KQ1sCsjLOVsnEYwV4HeQZ43LA89ucp7fqVfA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I love this place. Spent many days \u0026 nights over a course of 7 years at this place. My home away from home. Rustic Quiet charm and the family that owns it are wonderful.  Staff will go out of their way to assist at all possible. Food presentation is delightful and the food is delicious. Price and selection is good, atmosphere is off the charts if you r looking for something romantic, quiet and a  Israeli experience with true comfort, u must experience this place.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM5k2mP3LHH7tvpZcRlcfFaCKJTs4vc-KyIxnEl\u0026fid=0x0:0x13396909d82c2eff"],"When":"2020-6-23"},{"Name":"Nati Yakunina","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV2ZRyxpBFyf-69fHZ270s3B4iQB7GTzvAkwYH0psuwL_zQ6Rx_=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Marvellous view, it's like ,a piece of Italy in Israel. We stopped just for a cup of tea and sweet treat, the food is delicious. This place is in my list, I will definitely come back there.","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Sam Aberman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWW8LD98tdvZGX2GSpZHvoTTtCKd8qb17YM2nQsTU6mmb_xz9uN7Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba8-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Popped in with a couple of friends for dinner just before Jewish New year.
The place was very quiet and we had an extremely attentive service and a very enjoyable evening with the place almost entirely to ourselves.
As many others have stated, the beer selection from across the globe, is fantastic.
We had plenty of explanation and recommendation for beer choice - we tried quite a few and can't say we were disappointed by anything that was recommended.
The food was also great. Large portions and reasonably priced.
Over all a great experience and highly recommended place to visit.
They were counting down days for Octoberfest beer festival. No doubt it will be a different and much more busy and likely even more fun experience.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPmdRdOuPQ7gct4RuDF74tsEn8EViPSDTVAPkJo&fid=0x0:0x8af68f3aafebe741"],"When":"2022-9-28"},{"Name":"henry gild","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXmjKKz2QMKMA8svIC-FZ0kXPgRWHebnWrbNpdcywgjM4ewhj-GKQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Been there before with excellent service and food. This time the reception was lacking. I requested not to bring the main course until finished the starters and suddenly my wife order appeared. It was badly received  when I asked for it to be removed. I then received a total wrong order and when my order arrived it was not like previous times. On asking for a a salad they brought the wrong one and then removed it later returning it it as a takeaway.  The bill had items on it not ordered. The waitress was short tempered. Despite the fact that the food was good I will not return to Pinta nor recommend  it.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Analiza Tirazona","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUpg_3JlRjXVNa71HuGdTpLuUPcE7y08DvG-mzjcP5h6-d9ppl7gg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We went there to have my birthday lkunch, ,Service staffs are friendly, great  food, big  servings, good in house beers.. lovely place","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNCB9eycYp17BY8bqakZttpGQQn0G51FGkVnUrO&fid=0x0:0x8af68f3aafebe741"],"When":"2022-11-17"},{"Name":"Julka Szczygiel","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX8ApcaeQIAZogSCSDFIQ_6STkQ56gaBuqh8KnaOm7-bmcz8UYU=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The best meat, lamb ribs were delicious, cesar salad also. Highly recomended","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOMnMKOgbegyiNJhTUyzBHzTFKhHFBSOQmyCwmJ&fid=0x0:0x8af68f3aafebe741"],"When":"2021-7-29"},{"Name":"Abigail Karpil","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJYCtfaCJ6pNF61IaPniEjDfeVUrQ0j521IW4YtSdOyjJ0kYw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The place is nice has a unique pub-y like atmosphere. Service was slpw because there was only one lady serving that evening. We took the Grilled Salmon, which was a success, very recommended (89 shekels), the tongue, the shrimps which were also good. The pasta and the salad were great, however the pizza wasn't that good.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP_XhLJFyIWcWMkuKXFyA2281dbXDjlDcfc1q5d&fid=0x0:0x20328ed744140eba"],"When":"2023-5-28"},{"Name":"Dmitry Kopin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWWT8sILsCZ49bTwFShAFnVWnNkQy1x1AxKgbGmb1_ayV1oIbI=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"The hostess informed us that there were no available seats in the interior of the establishment, despite the fact that there were indeed seats available. We repeatedly expressed our discomfort with the outdoor seating due to the high temperatures and requested that the air conditioning unit be moved closer to our table. However, we were politely informed that it was not possible to relocate the air conditioning unit from another table, which was equipped with three air conditioning units.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"dani shemesh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWdgSl_GRV7eyiNlwct0sd-OjxjjMkJWc70QeJg446SMTwJiL1d=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"TL;DR the only coffee place in the park.

Joy garden has a winning location overlookingÂ the lake.
There are tables inside and outside underÂ  big ficus trees where you can enjoy the park air in spring and fall.

We got there for a late breakfast since it's the only place to buy food/drinks in the park. It's alwaysÂ full and you need to reserve a table ahead of time.
We got seatedÂ outside and got the menusÂ right away.
We ordered:
- Breakfast for one - omelet with salads, bread bucket and a drink.
- Croque madam - a fried egg in a bagelÂ with cheese.
- Porridge with fruitsÂ on top.
- Cappuccino and Americano to help us wake up :)

We got the drinks right away but the service is very slow there we waitedÂ over 30 min for the food, but the weather was good so we took our time.
The drinks were good but the food was medium - that's what happens when you have no competitionÂ .
The prices are fair - 180 nis tip inclusive.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPKcC0I7eGK_PKeDNoIEVs6gzzPrbUbWhfdywmQ&fid=0x0:0x20328ed744140eba"],"When":"2022-4-29"},{"Name":"Marc Berman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU2KT2XvYKolgMxa38doiRuKpqkNNKD3XWZdAH2ziRwTpuLDlgHqA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This hidden gem tucked away in the middle of a huge park has views looking over a lake and offers both a breakfast and dinner menu based on fish and dairy products. We arrived for breakfast and ordered the classic shakshuka, croque madame, Turkish pastry with spinach and the lentil, mushrooms and sweet potato salad. All 4 dishes were excellent and the accompanying side dishes were a nice touch. The bread was fresh and hot and the coffee finished off one of the best breakfast experiences here in Israel. We are looking forward to returning soon to experience the new evening fish menu.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPdyahsF4xaizl2WnLJF1r-VNB9I_5dImo502rN&fid=0x0:0x20328ed744140eba"],"When":"2023-7-11"},{"Name":"Ron Kitay","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVPbUGSYHwl7X6gHKMXkMbAvFwBspn6MvFflelRiJ3FN6bhVPgLug=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The food was tasty and fresh, the service was kind and attentful and the atmosphere was pleasant - we enjoyed our breakfast very much and we will definitely return.","Images":null,"When":""}]

It was quite busy so we had to wait a long time for the menu, ordering, food, etc. Nevertheless, people are friendly and it is a nice place to sit outside and enjoy the lively streets of Tel Aviv.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO9w8oVPjBPwAKY3gAxM8s1v3pBHYRUp3mQUHPV&fid=0x0:0x79369abaab6923ff"],"When":"2023-5-22"},{"Name":"Noam Firuz","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUM6T6K3RQONRCfyxAZw6JE0UyWLQxqNhTpjfOVkaOs0ilWw0Qt=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Awesome place!
.
1) The staff are very friendly and kind.
2) The food was delicious, I ate the Avocado & Salmon sandwich, it was absolutely amazing.
They use very good bread.
3) The location is great, and the music are definitely set up some good vibes.

Plus, I came to work with my laptop, and they are very friendly regarding people who comes to work and enjoy nice atmosphere.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNZ1CD4Nv6D69qQdlZZaioWmvDGTuCMNwHiami-&fid=0x0:0x79369abaab6923ff"],"When":"2017-12-8"},{"Name":"Ananas","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXvSY_0CcUHWW58CoAUab3IYnP5xLLWeIrwgd1uwzIiikBw9XI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great place for brunch with amazing local specialties. This place is right off Shuck HaCarmel so perfect for a little pause while you are visiting.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMM71bCG7xFn5fsQJeMeL-D823KSNotH30_63E9&fid=0x0:0x79369abaab6923ff"],"When":"2019-7-14"},{"Name":"Thanh Huyen Nguyen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVDKNOk_3Qqvaa5dp_a_fIqnpaWVcSmVs49tdyW9e1qOkiZOs_aDA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I ordered only Meze and acai bowl with ice coffee.
